Usage: cardano-cli conway governance action view --action-file FILEPATH
                                                   [ --output-json
                                                   | --output-yaml
                                                   ]
                                                   [--out-file FILEPATH]

  View a governance action.

Available options:
  --action-file FILEPATH   Path to action file.
  --output-json            Format governance action view output to JSON
                           (default).
  --output-yaml            Format governance action view output to YAML.
  --out-file FILEPATH      Optional output file. Default is to write to stdout.
  -h,--help                Show this help text
